Date: Thu, 5 Mar 2026 21:12:49 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] Glycan inverse design engine (position-specific OH
 contacts)

glycan/inverse_design.py:
  - SUGAR_POSITIONS: per-carbon OH type for Glc/Gal/Man/GlcNAc/GalNAc/
    2dGlc/Fru/Xyl/Fuc (4C1 conformation, literature stereochemistry)
  - _score_pocket_sugar(): position-specific desolv + HB + CH-pi scoring
  - design_glycan_pocket(): enumerate all contact subsets, rank by
    selectivity gap over interferents
  - Archetype library: Davis GluHUT, Trp cavity, Phe/Tyr cleft,
    H-bond array, macrocyclic cage

Key results:
  Glc (A-grade): contacts [C2,C4] + 2HB + 3xTrp-CHpi
    gap=-6.10 vs GlcNAc, -3.90 vs Gal, -3.90 vs Man
  Gal (A-grade, caveat): contacts [C1,C2] + 2HB + 3xTrp-CHpi
    gap=-6.10 vs GlcNAc, -3.90 vs Man; Gal/Glc degenerate (C4 not contacted)
  GlcNAc (B-grade): contacts [C1,C4] + 2HB + 3xTrp-CHpi
    gap=-3.90 vs Gal; GlcNAc/Glc/Man degenerate (C2-NAC not exploited)
  Man (B-grade): same structural note as GlcNAc
